WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:02.460
Is your family big, Tony?

00:03.100 --> 00:04.600
Yes, it is.

00:05.200 --> 00:06.200
Look!

00:06.700 --> 00:09.400
This is a photo of my family.

00:10.400 --> 00:12.800
These are my grandparents.

00:13.900 --> 00:16.400
These are my two grandfathers

00:16.700 --> 00:18.800
and my two grandmothers.

00:19.600 --> 00:22.700
My mum's parents are on the left

00:23.200 --> 00:26.700
and my dad's parents are on the right.

00:27.700 --> 00:30.100
These are my two uncles

00:30.700 --> 00:33.100
and this is my aunt.

00:33.700 --> 00:35.700
Is this your sister?

00:36.300 --> 00:40.700
Yes, this is my sister at the front.

00:41.500 --> 00:43.500
Her name's Linda.

